- Consider using mpy cross to cross compile the libraries before uploading.
    - Get uPy release:
        sys.implementation.version
        os.uname().release
    - Get uPy version ("language"):
        sys.implementation._mpy & 0xFF (from here: https://github.com/micropython/micropython/blob/master/tools/mpremote/mpremote/mip.py#L141)
- Package mpremote as binary.
- Think about name clashes in multiple package indices.
- Add support for packages without package.json (override in index)
- Handle error for missing package.json by suggesting to add it